======================
SVDRP client for xbmc
======================

Based on vdrpylib-0.3, python library for Video Disk Recorder (VDR)
The address of the original library
Version 0.2: https://sourceforge.net/projects/vdrpylib/files/
Version 0.3: http://people.debian.org/ ~ tschmidt / maemo / chinook / vdrpylib /

Introduction
------------

This is an interface for XBMC that allows communication with VDR through the protocol SVDRP VDR.
SVDRP: http://www.linuxtv.org/vdrwiki/index.php/SVDRP
For the momment is functionnal :
* The program guide, function *lste* SVDRP
* The programming, function *lstt* SVDRP
* The records, function *lstr* SVDRP (ongoing)
